  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Women recently diagnosed with Breast Cancer

          -  Will be undergoing surgery (after study) at the Hospital of the University of
             Pennsylvania

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Contraindications to MRI

          -  previously diagnosed with breast cancer (in the smae breast) within the past 5 years

          -  Patients with known locally advanced cancer (prior to study entry) being treated with
             preoperative adjuvant therapy.

          -  Pregnant women
      </textblock>
